                                    <condition>Minor stains to the last leaves. Some leaves have lost some gold, e.g. <locus from="13r" to="13r" scheme="folios"/>. Ink faded on some leaves, e.g. <locus from="63r" to="63r" scheme="folios"/>.</condition>
